-- Saccomanni Sees 40 Billion Euros of Arrears Paid in 12 Months
-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e
-- 2013-07-19T06:19:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-19/saccomanni-sees-40-billion-euros-of-arrears-paid-in-12-months.html
Italian Finance Minister Fabrizio
Saccomanni said the government will repay 40 billion euros of
corporate arrears within 12 months. He spoke on Bloomberg
Television in Moscow today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
